{"tid":506471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城開P哥帥嘆酒攬女 球員恥笑紅魔輸波","createTime":"2017-12-22T09:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T10:51:04.000Z","uid":4661,"like":85,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"60af5db2d997872e87c2616424d53198103dc3b2","tid":506471,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930398_38dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930398_38dd.jpg&h=f38004e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930399_8801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930399_8801.jpg&h=3f4fb7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930401_b13d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930401_b13d.jpg&h=1254fbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930402_84e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930402_84e2.jpg&h=41a71b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930404_917c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930404_917c.jpg&h=03cd4aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼市雙雄嘅敵對關係，似乎自從哥迪奧拿和摩連奴相繼入主後更趨惡劣。周三晚上，曼城逾500名職球員在曼切斯特市中心一間高級酒吧開聖誕Party，一眾球星包括阿古路、加比爾捷西斯和受傷的班捷文文迪均有通宵狂歡，就連主帥哥迪奧拿亦一邊品嚐紅酒，一邊「攬女」合照。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提嘅係，當晚同一時間有比賽嘅曼聯，意外係聯賽盃被英冠嘅布里斯托城絕殺出局，酒吧內立即隨即傳來巨大嘅歡呼聲，有目擊者更表示，曼城的職球員毫不掩飾對曼聯輸波嘅喜悅，不斷大聲嘲笑。看來曼市雙雄嘅關係，已去到水火不容嘅地步。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77cb472cac849a8d4e9414e82b525613d9b1431","tid":506471,"uid":26959,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"好唔尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca80b664f410f6677f444a643ec6be35e0f2f82e","tid":506471,"uid":34962,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930398_38dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930398_38dd.jpg&h=f38004e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930399_8801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930399_8801.jpg&h=3f4fb7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930401_b13d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930401_b13d.jpg&h=1254fbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513930402_84e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513930402_84e2.jpg&h=41a71b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/15139